  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to children of Farmers, Tamil Nadu</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The vulnerability of farmers of Tamil Nadu, due to drought makes the lives of their children more vulnerable to become child labour, school dropout, develop unhygienic behavior and live in an unprotective environment.  The government schools with poor infrastructure facilities discourage the children and parents. This project improves infrastructure in government schools and provide life skills to children of farmers, empower them to fight the challenge farmers face today.</narrative>
  </description>
